sql_query.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM "statuses" INNER JOIN "status_trends" ON "status_trends"."status_id" = "statuses"."id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "accounts" ON "accounts"."id" = "statuses"."account_id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "media_attachments" ON "media_attachments"."status_id" = "statuses"."id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "mentions" ON "mentions"."silent" = $1 AND "mentions"."status_id" = "statuses"."id" WHERE "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL LIMIT $2 OFFSET $3
